  <qti-item-body>
    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices="1" response-identifier="RESPONSE">
      <qti-prompt data-catalog-idref="tts_prompt">
        <p>Which is the correct order of Freytag's stages?</p>
      </qti-prompt>
      <qti-simple-choice fixed="true" identifier="A">
        <div data-catalog-idref="tts_choice_A">
          <p>Climax, exposition, rising action, resolution, falling action</p>
        </div>
        <qti-feedback-block identifier="feedback_A" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
          <qti-content-body>
            <div class="tb-feedback-incorrect" data-catalog-idref="feedback_A">
              <p>Not quite. A story can't open at its turning point — one stage has to set up the characters and their world before anything can build.</p>
            </div>
          </qti-content-body>
        </qti-feedback-block>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice fixed="true" identifier="B">
        <div data-catalog-idref="tts_choice_B">
          <p>Resolution, falling action, climax, rising action, exposition</p>
        </div>
        <qti-feedback-block identifier="feedback_B" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
          <qti-content-body>
            <div class="tb-feedback-incorrect" data-catalog-idref="feedback_B">
              <p>This lists the stages in reverse. A story can't open with everything already settled and the loose ends tied.</p>
            </div>
          </qti-content-body>
        </qti-feedback-block>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice fixed="true" identifier="C">
        <div data-catalog-idref="tts_choice_C">
          <p>Exposition, rising action, climax, falling action, resolution</p>
        </div>
        <qti-feedback-block identifier="feedback_C" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
          <qti-content-body>
            <div class="tb-feedback-correct" data-catalog-idref="feedback_C">
              <p>Correct! Freytag's order is exposition, rising action, climax, falling action, resolution.</p>
            </div>
          </qti-content-body>
        </qti-feedback-block>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice fixed="true" identifier="D">
        <div data-catalog-idref="tts_choice_D">
          <p>Rising action, exposition, resolution, climax, falling action</p>
        </div>
        <qti-feedback-block identifier="feedback_D" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
          <qti-content-body>
            <div class="tb-feedback-incorrect" data-catalog-idref="feedback_D">
              <p>The tension can't start climbing before we've met the characters — and the turning point can't land after things have settled.</p>
            </div>
          </qti-content-body>
        </qti-feedback-block>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
